item.title: Majozi
item.description: Majozi chats to Texx about the songs that for him embody the spirit of South Africa, the exciting technical developments with his set, and how stoked he is to be a part of Halfway Group’s new campaign “On Track To Better”. Feed: https://texxtalks.libsyn.com/rss
